---
import Body from '../layouts/Body.astro';
import image from '../assets/images/introduction.png';
---

<Body>
  <div>
    <h3>Instant group Chats</h3>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo
      ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis
      dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculua mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies
      nec, pellentesque eu, pretium quis, sem. Nulla consequat massa
